### ============================================================
### WeatherFiesta API — JetBrains HTTP Client
### ============================================================
### Usage: Open in Rider/IntelliJ, run the login request first,
### then run any other request. The token is captured automatically.
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@token = {{login.response.body.$.access_token}}

### Deterministic IDs from WeatherFiesta.IntegrationTests TestData.
### London and Paris are seeded; Berlin is defined for create/unsubscribed scenarios.
@cityId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
@cityId1 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
@cityId2 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000020
@cityId3 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000030
@userId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001


### ============================================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================================

### Login — get access token (FakeIdentityProvider)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/_system/identity/connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password
&client_id=weatherfiesta-api
&username=luke.skywalker@starwars.com
&password=starwars
&scope=openid profile email roles

### ============================================================
### CITY ENDPOINTS (api/core/cities)
### ============================================================

### City Suggestions — search via geocoding
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/suggestions?search=Berlin&countryCode=DE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create City — create and subscribe
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Berlin",
  "countryCode": "DE"
}

### List User Cities — all subscriptions with weather
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Unsubscribe from City
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/{{cityId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Set Primary City
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/{{cityId}}/primary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Reorder Cities
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  "{{cityId1}}",
  "{{cityId2}}",
  "{{cityId3}}"
]

### City Weather — current + forecast
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/{{cityId}}/weather?forecastDays=7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Trigger Weather Ingestion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/{{cityId}}/ingest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ============================================================
### WEATHER ENDPOINTS (api/core/cities)
### ============================================================

### Weather Alerts — all subscribed cities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Sunrise/Sunset Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/{{cityId}}/sun?days=7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Compare Weather Across Cities
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/compare
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  "{{cityId1}}",
  "{{cityId2}}"
]

### Export All Cities Weather (CSV)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Export City Forecast (CSV)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/{{cityId}}/weather/export?days=7
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Weather Recommendations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/cities/{{cityId}}/recommendations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ============================================================
### USER ENDPOINTS (api/core/users)
### ============================================================

### Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update User Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/core/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Luke Skywalker",
  "email": "luke@rebel-alliance.org"
}

### Get User Preferences
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/users/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update User Preferences
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/core/users/preferences
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "temperatureUnit": "Celsius",
  "windSpeedUnit": "Kmh"
}

### Delete User (soft-delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/core/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ============================================================
### DASHBOARD ENDPOINT
### ============================================================

### Get Dashboard — cities, highlights, alerts, recommendations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ============================================================
### ADMIN ENDPOINTS (api/core/admin/cities) — Administrators role required
### ============================================================

### Admin — Create City (no geocoding)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/cities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Berlin",
  "country": "Germany",
  "countryCode": "DE",
  "latitude": 52.52,
  "longitude": 13.405,
  "timeZone": "Europe/Berlin",
  "elevation": 34.0
}

### Admin — Update City
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/cities/{{cityId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Berlin",
  "country": "Germany",
  "countryCode": "DE",
  "latitude": 52.52,
  "longitude": 13.405,
  "timeZone": "Europe/Berlin",
  "elevation": 34.0
}

### Admin — Delete City (hard-delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/cities/{{cityId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin — List All Cities with subscription counts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/cities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin — List City Subscriptions (incl. soft-deleted)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/cities/{{cityId}}/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin — Trigger Weather Ingestion (no subscription check)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/cities/{{cityId}}/ingest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin — Reset City Weather Data
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/cities/{{cityId}}/weather
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin — Delete User (hard-delete WeatherFiesta data)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ============================================================
### SUBSCRIPTION ENDPOINTS
### ============================================================

### Get Current User Subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/users/subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin — List All User Subscriptions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin — Get User Subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/subscriptions/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Admin — Update User Subscription
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/core/admin/subscriptions/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "Pro",
  "status": "Active",
  "billingCycle": "Monthly"
}


### ============================================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/healthz
